trans-unit.source: Represents a Microsoft Office Outlook form region that is based on an Outlook Form Storage (*.ofs) file.
trans-unit.target: 表示基于 Outlook 窗体存储 (*.ofs) 文件的 Microsoft Office Outlook 窗体区域。

trans-unit.source: Visual Studio generates an instance of a class that implements the <xref:Microsoft.Office.Tools.Outlook.ImportedFormRegion> interface when you import a form region from Outlook into Visual Studio.
trans-unit.target: Visual Studio 将生成的类的实现实例<xref:Microsoft.Office.Tools.Outlook.ImportedFormRegion>接口从 Outlook 窗体区域导入 Visual Studio 时。

trans-unit.source: In most cases, you do not have to use this class directly.
trans-unit.target: 在大多数情况下，无需直接使用此类。

trans-unit.source: Instead, you can use the form region class that Visual Studio generates when you import the form region.
trans-unit.target: 相反，你可以使用 Visual Studio 将生成时导入窗体区域的窗体区域类。

trans-unit.source: The form region class inherits from <xref:Microsoft.Office.Tools.Outlook.ImportedFormRegionBase>.
trans-unit.target: 窗体区域类继承自<xref:Microsoft.Office.Tools.Outlook.ImportedFormRegionBase>。

trans-unit.source: You can accomplish most tasks related to the form region by using the events and properties in the form region class.
trans-unit.target: 你可以完成通过使用窗体区域类中的事件和属性相关联到窗体区域的大多数任务。

trans-unit.source: If you want to work with the <xref:Microsoft.Office.Tools.Outlook.ImportedFormRegion> directly, call the <xref:Microsoft.Office.Tools.Outlook.ImportedFormRegionBase.Base%2A> property of the <xref:Microsoft.Office.Tools.Outlook.ImportedFormRegionBase> class.
trans-unit.target: 如果你想要使用<xref:Microsoft.Office.Tools.Outlook.ImportedFormRegion>直接调用<xref:Microsoft.Office.Tools.Outlook.ImportedFormRegionBase.Base%2A>属性<xref:Microsoft.Office.Tools.Outlook.ImportedFormRegionBase>类。

trans-unit.source: Usage
trans-unit.target: 用法

trans-unit.source: Gets the default extension for this <see cref="T:Microsoft.Office.Tools.Outlook.ImportedFormRegion" /> object.
trans-unit.target: 获取此 <see cref="T:Microsoft.Office.Tools.Outlook.ImportedFormRegion" /> 对象的默认扩展。

trans-unit.source: The default extension for this <see cref="T:Microsoft.Office.Tools.Outlook.ImportedFormRegion" /> object.
trans-unit.target: 此 <see cref="T:Microsoft.Office.Tools.Outlook.ImportedFormRegion" /> 对象的默认扩展。

trans-unit.source: The default extension is an <xref:Microsoft.Office.Tools.Outlook.IImportedFormRegionExtension> object that is implemented by the [!INCLUDE[vsto_runtime](~/includes/vsto-runtime-md.md)].
trans-unit.target: 默认扩展名是<xref:Microsoft.Office.Tools.Outlook.IImportedFormRegionExtension>对象由实现[!INCLUDE[vsto_runtime](~/includes/vsto-runtime-md.md)]。

trans-unit.source: Gets a custom extension for this <see cref="T:Microsoft.Office.Tools.Outlook.ImportedFormRegion" /> object.
trans-unit.target: 获取此 <see cref="T:Microsoft.Office.Tools.Outlook.ImportedFormRegion" /> 对象的自定义扩展。

trans-unit.source: A custom extension for this <see cref="T:Microsoft.Office.Tools.Outlook.ImportedFormRegion" /> object.
trans-unit.target: 此 <see cref="T:Microsoft.Office.Tools.Outlook.ImportedFormRegion" /> 对象的自定义扩展。

trans-unit.source: A custom extension is an implementation of the <xref:Microsoft.Office.Tools.Outlook.IImportedFormRegionExtension> interface in a solution that is created by using the Office development tools in Visual Studio.
trans-unit.target: 自定义扩展是一种实现的<xref:Microsoft.Office.Tools.Outlook.IImportedFormRegionExtension>通过使用 Visual Studio 中的 Office 开发工具创建的解决方案中的接口。

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the form region factory that is associated with this <see cref="T:Microsoft.Office.Tools.Outlook.ImportedFormRegion" />.
trans-unit.target: 获取或设置与此 <see cref="T:Microsoft.Office.Tools.Outlook.ImportedFormRegion" /> 关联的窗体区域工厂。

trans-unit.source: An object that implements the <see cref="T:Microsoft.Office.Tools.Outlook.IFormRegionFactory" /> interface.
trans-unit.target: 一个实现 <see cref="T:Microsoft.Office.Tools.Outlook.IFormRegionFactory" /> 接口的对象。

trans-unit.source: You can use this property to track the form region factory class that created the current instance of the <xref:Microsoft.Office.Tools.Outlook.ImportedFormRegion>.
trans-unit.target: 你可以使用此属性来跟踪创建的当前实例的窗体区域工厂类<xref:Microsoft.Office.Tools.Outlook.ImportedFormRegion>。

trans-unit.source: For more information about how to create an instance of an <xref:Microsoft.Office.Tools.Outlook.ImportedFormRegion>, see the <xref:Microsoft.Office.Tools.Outlook.IFormRegionFactory.CreateFormRegion%2A> method of the <xref:Microsoft.Office.Tools.Outlook.IFormRegionFactory> interface.
trans-unit.target: 有关如何创建的实例的详细信息<xref:Microsoft.Office.Tools.Outlook.ImportedFormRegion>，请参阅<xref:Microsoft.Office.Tools.Outlook.IFormRegionFactory.CreateFormRegion%2A>方法<xref:Microsoft.Office.Tools.Outlook.IFormRegionFactory>接口。

trans-unit.source: Occurs before the form region is closed.
trans-unit.target: 在窗体区域关闭之前发生。

trans-unit.source: To get the Microsoft Office Outlook item for which the form region appears, call the <xref:Microsoft.Office.Tools.Outlook.ImportedFormRegion.OutlookItem%2A> property.
trans-unit.target: 若要获取窗体区域将显示 Microsoft Office Outlook 项，请调用<xref:Microsoft.Office.Tools.Outlook.ImportedFormRegion.OutlookItem%2A>属性。

trans-unit.source: To get the Inspector that displays the Outlook item, call the <xref:Microsoft.Office.Tools.Outlook.ImportedFormRegion.OutlookFormRegion%2A> to get an instance of the <xref:Microsoft.Office.Interop.Outlook.FormRegion?displayProperty=fullName>, and then call the [Microsoft.Office.Interop.Outlook.FormRegion.Inspector](http://msdn.microsoft.com/en-us/library/microsoft.office.interop.outlook._formregion.inspector.aspx) property of the <xref:Microsoft.Office.Interop.Outlook.FormRegion?displayProperty=fullName> object.
trans-unit.target: 若要获取显示的 Outlook 项的检查器，请调用<xref:Microsoft.Office.Tools.Outlook.ImportedFormRegion.OutlookFormRegion%2A>要获取其实例的<xref:Microsoft.Office.Interop.Outlook.FormRegion?displayProperty=fullName>，然后调用[Microsoft.Office.Interop.Outlook.FormRegion.Inspector](http://msdn.microsoft.com/en-us/library/microsoft.office.interop.outlook._formregion.inspector.aspx)属性<xref:Microsoft.Office.Interop.Outlook.FormRegion?displayProperty=fullName>对象。

trans-unit.source: Occurs after an instance of the form region is created but before the form region appears.
trans-unit.target: 在创建窗体区域的实例之后且在窗体区域显示之前发生。

trans-unit.source: To get the Outlook item for which the form region appears, call the <xref:Microsoft.Office.Tools.Outlook.ImportedFormRegion.OutlookItem%2A> property.
trans-unit.target: 若要获取为其显示窗体区域的 Outlook 项，请调用<xref:Microsoft.Office.Tools.Outlook.ImportedFormRegion.OutlookItem%2A>属性。

trans-unit.source: To get the Inspector that displays the Outlook item, call the <xref:Microsoft.Office.Tools.Outlook.ImportedFormRegion.OutlookFormRegion%2A> to get an instance of the <xref:Microsoft.Office.Interop.Outlook.FormRegion?displayProperty=fullName>, and then call the [Microsoft.Office.Interop.Outlook.FormRegion.Inspector](http://msdn.microsoft.com/en-us/library/microsoft.office.interop.outlook._formregion.inspector.aspx) property of the <xref:Microsoft.Office.Interop.Outlook.FormRegion?displayProperty=fullName> object.
trans-unit.target: 若要获取显示的 Outlook 项的检查器，请调用<xref:Microsoft.Office.Tools.Outlook.ImportedFormRegion.OutlookFormRegion%2A>要获取其实例的<xref:Microsoft.Office.Interop.Outlook.FormRegion?displayProperty=fullName>，然后调用[Microsoft.Office.Interop.Outlook.FormRegion.Inspector](http://msdn.microsoft.com/en-us/library/microsoft.office.interop.outlook._formregion.inspector.aspx)属性<xref:Microsoft.Office.Interop.Outlook.FormRegion?displayProperty=fullName>对象。

trans-unit.source: The name of the control that you would like to locate in the <see langword="Microsoft.Vbe.Interop.Forms.UserForm" /> of the form region.
trans-unit.target: 您将在窗体区域的 <see langword="Microsoft.Vbe.Interop.Forms.UserForm" /> 中定位到的控件的名称。

trans-unit.source: Returns the specified control from the <c>Microsoft.Vbe.Interop.Forms.UserForm</c> of the form region.
trans-unit.target: 从表单区域的 <c>Microsoft.Vbe.Interop.Forms.UserForm</c> 返回指定控件。

trans-unit.source: The control that is specified by <paramref name="identifier" />.
trans-unit.target: <paramref name="identifier" /> 指定的控件。

trans-unit.source: If you manually create a form region class that inherits from <xref:Microsoft.Office.Tools.Outlook.ImportedFormRegion>, call this method to return each control that is identified in the Outlook Form Storage (*.ofs) file from the `Microsoft.Vbe.Interop.Forms.UserForm` of the native form region.
trans-unit.target: 如果你手动创建继承自的窗体区域类<xref:Microsoft.Office.Tools.Outlook.ImportedFormRegion>，调用此方法以返回从 Outlook 窗体存储 (*.ofs) 文件中标识的每个控件`Microsoft.Vbe.Interop.Forms.UserForm`的本机窗体区域。

trans-unit.source: The form region specified by the <see cref="P:Microsoft.Office.Tools.Outlook.ImportedFormRegion.OutlookFormRegion" /> property is <see langword="null" />.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="P:Microsoft.Office.Tools.Outlook.ImportedFormRegion.OutlookFormRegion" /> 属性所指定的窗体区域为 <see langword="null" />。

trans-unit.source: *Identifier* does not match a control in the .ofs file.
trans-unit.target: 标识符与 .ofs 文件中的控件不匹配。

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the native form region object.
trans-unit.target: 获取或设置本机窗体区域对象。

trans-unit.source: A <see cref="T:Microsoft.Office.Interop.Outlook.FormRegion" /> that represents the form region.
trans-unit.target: 一个表示窗体区域的 <see cref="T:Microsoft.Office.Interop.Outlook.FormRegion" />。

trans-unit.source: You can call the [Microsoft.Office.Interop.Outlook.FormRegion.Inspector](http://msdn.microsoft.com/en-us/library/microsoft.office.interop.outlook._formregion.inspector.aspx) property of the <xref:Microsoft.Office.Interop.Outlook.FormRegion?displayProperty=fullName> object to get an instance of the Inspector that displays the form region.
trans-unit.target: 你可以调用[Microsoft.Office.Interop.Outlook.FormRegion.Inspector](http://msdn.microsoft.com/en-us/library/microsoft.office.interop.outlook._formregion.inspector.aspx)属性<xref:Microsoft.Office.Interop.Outlook.FormRegion?displayProperty=fullName>要获取的检查器显示窗体区域的实例对象。

trans-unit.source: Gets the Microsoft Office Outlook item for which the form region appears.
trans-unit.target: 获取为其显示窗体区域的 Microsoft Office Outlook 项。

trans-unit.source: An <see cref="T:System.Object" /> that represents the Outlook item for which the form region appears.
trans-unit.target: 一个 <see cref="T:System.Object" />，表示为其显示窗体区域的 Outlook 项。

trans-unit.source: Cast the object to the item type that the form region is associated with.
trans-unit.target: 强制转换到窗体区域关联的项类型的对象。

trans-unit.source: For example, if the form region is associated with a contact item, cast the object that is returned by the <xref:Microsoft.Office.Tools.Outlook.ImportedFormRegion.OutlookItem%2A> property to a <xref:Microsoft.Office.Interop.Outlook.ContactItem>.
trans-unit.target: 例如，如果窗体区域与联系人项目相关联，将对象强制转换返回<xref:Microsoft.Office.Tools.Outlook.ImportedFormRegion.OutlookItem%2A>属性<xref:Microsoft.Office.Interop.Outlook.ContactItem>。
